      "expected_tags": "Subset check. For red-tier techniques, tag detection may vary between KataGo runs.",
      "level_id_range": "Difficulty band. Ranges are wide (±2-5 levels) to absorb KataGo variance of ±1 level.",
      "min_refutations": "Floor check. Set to 0 for techniques where refutation generation is unreliable (ko, seki, ladder, net, capture-race, snapback, corner).",
      "expect_teaching_comments": "Currently false for all entries. Teaching comments should be validated via statistical batch tests, not per-fixture."
    }
  },
